2017年4月7日，[[叙利亚内战|叙利亚内战]]期间，美国海军从位于[[地中海|地中海]]的伯克级驱逐舰上发射了59枚[[战斧巡航导弹|战斧巡航导弹]]，打击位于[[叙利亚|叙利亚]]境内由[[叙利亚武装力量|叙利亚政府军]]控制的[[沙伊拉特空军基地|沙伊拉特空军基地]]<ref name="The Pentagon’s play-by-play of the Syria strikes" /><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.defense.gov/News/News-Releases/News-Release-View/Article/1144598/statement-from-pentagon-spokesman-capt-jeff-davis-on-us-strike-in-syria|title=Statement from Pentagon Spokesman Capt. Jeff Davis on U.S. strike in S|work=U.S. DEPARTMENT OF DEFENSE|access-date=2017-04-07|language=en-US|archive-date=2017-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407071200/https://www.defense.gov/News/News-Releases/News-Release-View/Article/1144598/statement-from-pentagon-spokesman-capt-jeff-davis-on-us-strike-in-syria|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="cnn-1">{{cite web|last1=Starr|first1=Barbara|last2=Diamond|first2=Jeremy|title=Trump launches military strike against Syria|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2017/04/06/politics/donald-trump-syria-military/index.html|website=[[CNN|CNN]]|publisher=[[Turner_Broadcasting_System|Turner Broadcasting System]] ([[Time_Warner|Time Warner]])|accessdate=7 April 2017|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407021906/http://edition.cnn.com/2017/04/06/politics/donald-trump-syria-military/index.html|archivedate=2017-04-07|date=6 April 2017|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="bbc-1">{{cite web|author1=''BBC News'' staff|title=Syria war: US launches missile strikes following chemical 'attack'|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-39523654|website=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|publisher=[[British_Broadcasting_Corporation|British Broadcasting Corporation]]|accessdate=7 April 2017|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407022056/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-39523654|archivedate=2017-04-07|date=7 April 2017|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[俄罗斯联邦国防部|俄罗斯联邦国防部]]随后统计，有23枚命中目标，其余36枚尚不得而知。隨後美軍所發布的偵察照片則顯示清晰的彈著點，59枚巡弋飛彈全部命中，並將機庫中的飛機及機場儲油設備摧毀。此次军事打击行动由美国总统[[唐纳德·特朗普|特朗普]]下令，以报复3天前，发生在汗谢洪的[[2017年汗谢洪化学武器袭击事件|化学武器袭击事件]]。<ref name="wapo-1">{{cite web|last1=Lamothe|first1=Dan|last2=Ryan|first2=Missy|last3=Gibbons-Neff|first3=Thomas|title=U.S. strikes Syrian military airfield in first direct assault on Bashar al-Assad’s government|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/national-security/trump-weighing-military-options-following-chemical-weapons-attack-in-syria/2017/04/06/0c59603a-1ae8-11e7-9887-1a5314b56a08_story.html?utm_term=.225bc956b60a|website=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|publisher=[[Jeff_Bezos|Nash Holdings LLC]]|accessdate=7 April 2017|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407024143/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/national-security/trump-weighing-military-options-following-chemical-weapons-attack-in-syria/2017/04/06/0c59603a-1ae8-11e7-9887-1a5314b56a08_story.html?utm_term=.8c07d2ab7210|archivedate=2017-04-07|date=6 April 2017|dead-url=no}}</ref>美国政府声称从该基地起飞的飞机，执行了针对平民的化学武器攻击，故而开展打击行动。这是美国首次有目的性地打击叙利亚境内的军事目标{{efn|name=上次空襲|上一次美国[[2016年美國聯軍空襲敘利亞政府軍事件|轰炸代尔祖尔机场]]，造成60名叙利亚军人死亡，美军称是误炸。}}<ref name="abc-au-1">{{cite web|author1=''ABC News'' staff|title=US warships launch cruise missile strike against Syrian airfield in retaliation for chemical attack|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2017-04-07/us-launches-cruise-missile-strike-on-syria/8425132|publisher=ABC News Australia|accessdate=7 April 2017|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407023424/http://www.abc.net.au/news/2017-04-07/us-launches-cruise-missile-strike-on-syria/8425132|archivedate=2017-04-07|date=7 April 2017|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 緣起 ==
在[[2017年汗谢洪化学武器袭击事件|汗谢洪化学武器袭击事件]]後，美國總統川普於4月5日指示[[美國國防部長|國防部長]][[詹姆士·馬提斯|詹姆士·馬提斯]]提出軍事選項應對這一事件，[[美國國防部|美國國防部]]於隔日提交了最終的行動計畫。而總統川普則於[[美東時間|美東時間]]4月6日16時30分批准對敘利亞[[沙伊拉特空軍基地|沙伊拉特空軍基地]]發動攻擊的计划。<ref name="The Pentagon’s play-by-play of the Syria strikes">{{cite news|author1=Aaron Mehta|title=The Pentagon’s play-by-play of the Syria strikes|url=http://www.defensenews.com/articles/syria-chemical-attack-us-response|accessdate=2017-04-09|publisher=defensenews|date=2017-04-07}}</ref>

==攻击==
