[[File:USS_Porter_Strikes_on_Syria_(518031).webm|thumb]]
2017年4月6日晚间，根据战争权限法，总统特朗普将打击叙利亚的计划知会[[美国国会|国会]]。<ref name="bloom">{{cite web| url =https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2017-04-07/can-the-president-attack-another-country-without-congress| title =Can the President Attack Another Country Without Congress?| publisher =[[Bloomberg_L.P.|Bloomberg L.P.]]| accessdate =7 April 2017| archive-date =2017-04-07| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20170407230607/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2017-04-07/can-the-president-attack-another-country-without-congress| dead-url =no}}</ref>根据白宫的声明，超过24名议员听取了简报。

空袭的目标是位于叙利亚[[霍姆斯省|霍姆斯省]]境内的[[沙伊拉特空军基地|沙伊拉特空军基地]]。这座机场有可能是4日发生在汗谢洪的化学武器袭击事件中，战斗机起降的机场。这次袭击的重点打击对象为机场的防空力量、战机、机库以及油料储备。当地时间凌晨4：40分两艘[[阿利·伯克級驅逐艦|伯克级驱逐舰]]参与了此次行动，分别为[[罗斯号驱逐舰_(DDG-71)|罗斯号 (DDG-71)]]和[[波特号驱逐舰_(DDG-78)|波特号 (DDG-78)]]，共计发射了60枚战斧巡航导弹，其中1顆落入水中。<ref name="wapo-1"/><ref name="The Pentagon’s play-by-play of the Syria strikes" />[[俄罗斯联邦国防部|俄罗斯联邦国防部]]随后统计，有23枚命中目标，其余36枚尚不得而知。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.latimes.com/world/middleeast/la-fg-syria-airstrike-20170406-story.html |title="Syria says several killed and wounded in U.S. airstrike on Syrian airfield", by Molly Hennessy-Fiske, ''Los Angeles Times'' |accessdate=2017-04-07 |archive-date=2017-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407102450/http://www.latimes.com/world/middleeast/la-fg-syria-airstrike-20170406-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[美国中央司令部|美国中央司令部]]在随后向媒体发出消息，行动摧毁了空军基地的战机、防御机库、石油和后勤储备、弹药库、机场防空系统和雷达。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.centcom.mil/MEDIA/PRESS-RELEASES/Press-Release-View/Article/1144711/statement-from-pentagon-spokesman-capt-jeff-davis-on-us-strike-in-syria/|title=Statement from Pentagon Spokesman Capt. Jeff Davis on U.S. strike in Syria|last=|first=|date=7 April 2017|website=U.S. Central Command|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407233354/http://www.centcom.mil/MEDIA/PRESS-RELEASES/Press-Release-View/Article/1144711/statement-from-pentagon-spokesman-capt-jeff-davis-on-us-strike-in-syria/|archive-date=2017-04-07|dead-url=no|access-date=7 April 2017}}</ref>一家俄罗斯电视台称，有9架飞机被摧毁，当时应该没有飞机在执行任务。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.itv.com/news/update/2017-04-07/syrian-planes-out-of-action-at-time-of-us-strike-on-airfield/|title=Nine Syrian planes destroyed by US strike on airfield|publisher=ITV News|date=7 April 2017|accessdate=2017-04-07|archive-date=2017-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407234043/http://www.itv.com/news/update/2017-04-07/syrian-planes-out-of-action-at-time-of-us-strike-on-airfield/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

美国在开展打击行动前，知会了一些国家，例如澳大利亚和俄罗斯。<ref name="ausfr-1">{{cite web|last1=Tingle|first1=Laura|title=Australia briefed beforehand on US strike|url=http://www.afr.com/news/policy/foreign-affairs/australia-briefed-beforehand-on-us-missile-strike-on-syria-20170407-gvfvi8|website=[[The_Australian_Financial_Review|The Australian Financial Review]]|publisher=[[Fairfax_Media|Fairfax Media]]|accessdate=7 April 2017|date=7 April 2017|archive-date=2017-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407030817/http://www.afr.com/news/policy/foreign-affairs/australia-briefed-beforehand-on-us-missile-strike-on-syria-20170407-gvfvi8|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="aljazeera-1">{{cite web|author1="Al Jazeera and news agencies"|title=US launches cruise missiles at Syrian air base|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2017/04/us-missiles-syria-170407013424492.html|website=[[Al_Jazeera|Al Jazeera]]|publisher=[[Al_Jazeera_Media_Network|Al Jazeera Media Network]]|accessdate=7 April 2017|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407030002/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2017/04/us-missiles-syria-170407013424492.html|archivedate=2017-04-07|date=7 April 2017|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="economictimes-1">{{cite web |author1=AFP |title=UN divided over Syria gas attack probe as US launches missile strike |url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/international/world-news/un-divided-over-syria-gas-attack-probe-as-us-launches-missile-strike/articleshow/58058642.cms |website=[[The_Economic_Times|The Economic Times]] |publisher=[[The_Times_Group|The Times Group]] |accessdate=7 April 2017 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20170407030423/http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/international/world-news/un-divided-over-syria-gas-attack-probe-as-us-launches-missile-strike/articleshow/58058642.cms |archivedate=2017-04-07 |date=7 April 2017 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>当时机场内可能有俄罗斯军人。叙利亚政府方面的报告统计，共有16人在这次袭击中死亡，其中7人为叙利亚士兵。<ref name="wsj_casualties"/>叙利亚人权观察组织称，这次空袭摧毁了一定数量的机库，一座油料库以及一座防空基地。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.idahostatesman.com/news/nation-world/article143257599.html|title=The Latest: Group says at least 4 killed in US Syria attack|work=idahostatesman|access-date=2017-04-07|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-mideast-crisis-syria-observatory-idUKKBN1790IO?il=0|title=Syrian monitor says airbase almost destroyed in strike|last=Editorial|first=Reuters|work=Reuters UK|access-date=2017-04-07|language=en-GB|archive-date=2017-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407233053/http://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-mideast-crisis-syria-observatory-idUKKBN1790IO?il=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>这是特朗普上任以来首次对效忠[[阿萨德|阿萨德]]政权的军事力量展开行动。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.dallasnews.com/news/world/2017/04/06/us-launches-missile-strike-syria|title=Trump calls on 'all civilized nations' to end carnage in Syria after launching missile strike|last=|first=|date=|website=Dallas News|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190216135938/https://www.dallasnews.com/news/world/2017/04/06/us-launches-missile-strike-syria|archive-date=2019-02-16|dead-url=no|access-date=}}</ref>

==后果==
空袭后国际金融市场反应明显，国际油价随即上涨2%。<ref name="cnbc-1">{{cite web|last1=Sile|first1=Aza Wee|last2=Ming|first2=Cheang|title=Oil jumps, dollar slightly weaker as US fires dozens of missiles at targets in Syria|url=http://www.cnbc.com/2017/04/06/higher-open-seen-for-asia-markets-as-trump-xi-summit-gets-underway-oil-gains-noted.html|website=[[CNBC|CNBC]]|publisher=NBCUniversal News Group|accessdate=7 April 2017|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407051150/http://www.cnbc.com/2017/04/06/higher-open-seen-for-asia-markets-as-trump-xi-summit-gets-underway-oil-gains-noted.html|archivedate=2017-04-07|date=7 April 2017|dead-url=no}}</ref>现货黄金跳涨近10美元。<ref>{{cite web|title=刚刚，美国发动大规模导弹袭击！金融市场炸了|url=http://news.cnfol.com/weishendu/20170407/24557016.shtml|publisher=中金在线|accessdate=7 April 2017|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170408082930/http://news.cnfol.com/weishendu/20170407/24557016.shtml|archivedate=2017年4月8日}}</ref>[[日元|日元]]作为避险货币，兑美元上涨0.46%。<ref>{{cite web|title=Dollar eases against the yen after US missile strike in Syria|url=http://www.cnbc.com/2017/04/06/dollar-eases-against-the-yen-after-us-missile-strike-in-syria.html|publisher=[[CNBC|CNBC]]|accessdate=7 April 2017|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112014305/https://www.cnbc.com/2017/04/06/dollar-eases-against-the-yen-after-us-missile-strike-in-syria.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>美国国内股市则普遍小幅下跌，但于次日涨回。

俄罗斯表示将和美国达成协定，以避免在空中的武装冲突。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2017-04-07/syria-strikes-why-did-donald-trump-target-that-airbase/8425658|title=Syria: Here's what you need to know about Trump's strike on air base|accessdate=2017-04-07|archive-date=2017-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170407053729/http://www.abc.net.au/news/2017-04-07/syria-strikes-why-did-donald-trump-target-that-airbase/8425658|dead-url=no}}</ref>俄罗斯国防部发言人称，将强化叙利亚境内的防空设施，为其境内的重要基础设施建设提供保护。<ref>{{cite web|title=Russia to strengthen Syrian air defences after US strikes|url=http://www.irishtimes.com/news/world/us/russia-to-strengthen-syrian-air-defences-after-us-strikes-1.3040228|publisher=[[The_Irish_Times|The Irish Times]]|accessdate=7 April 2017|archive-date=2019-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912135236/https://www.irishtimes.com/news/world/us/united-states-warns-we-re-prepared-to-do-more-in-syria-1.3040228|dead-url=no}}</ref>

霍姆斯省的政府官员表示，在霍姆斯省东部，[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]向政府军控制的战略石油储备发动了多轮攻击，但最终被击退。<ref>[https://www.rt.com/news/383826-isis-used-us-airstrike-syria/ ISIS used US missile strike to launch new offensive near Palmyra, Homs governor tells RT] {{Wayback|url=https://www.rt.com/news/383826-isis-used-us-airstrike-syria/ |date=20180123220425 }}. ''RT''. 2017-04-07.</ref><ref>[https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/isil-takes-advantage-us-attack-government-storm-western-palmyra/ ISIL takes advantage of US attack on government to storm western Palmyra] {{Wayback|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/isil-takes-advantage-us-attack-government-storm-western-palmyra/ |date=20190502060740 }}. ''AMN''. 7 April 2017</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/isil-takes-advantage-us-attack-government-storm-western-palmyra/ |title=ISIL takes advantage of US attack on government to storm western Palmyra |accessdate=2017-04-07 |archive-date=2019-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190502060740/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/isil-takes-advantage-us-attack-government-storm-western-palmyra/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

